TimeSensitiveLogic.Description: The Collect function depends on time conditions, specifically that current time exceeds acc.unlockTime before processing withdrawals.

ConditionalLogicPaths: The Put function sets unlockTime based on a conditional check, either setting it to _unlockTime or the current time.
The Collect function has conditional paths based on balance, unlock time, and minimum balance requirements, leading to either successful withdrawal or function reversion.
